---
title: Chorizo and Bacon Burgers with Roasted Wedges and Cilantro-Lime Mayo
description: A caliente combo of chorizo sausage and cilantro meet in this Mexican-inspired burger! Crispy potato wedges and a wholesome green salad make for satisfying sides.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-and-bacon-burgers-20c8b9f6.jpg
